General information
-------------------

JPHP is a simple yet powerfull Framework/Library for the popular PHP language.
It take its inspiration from Java classe organization and hierachy. JPHP has
those features:

- Java like classes import
- 100% Object Oriented, designed with refactoring and lots of design pattern
- Extensible : Make use lots of Abstract/Interface like approch
- Package library hierarchy/organisation in a Java way
- A coding standard : easy to learn, be 100% on your project but not on the 
  library use learning

  

